        ignoreInDialogue="true"
        location="anywhere"
        word="there are">
    <summary>Use of "[WORD]"</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[A passive construction that often adds words but little else to the sentence.  Where possible show the reader rather than tell.  <a href="https://writingcenter.unc.edu/tips-and-tools/passive-voice/">More details.</a>]]></description>
  </rule>
